### Vue 3 / Frontend
- script setup syntax always — no Options API
- Composables (use* prefix) for all reusable logic and data fetching
- Pinia for global state management (setup store pattern)
- TypeScript: typed props with defineProps<{...}>(), typed emits with defineEmits<{...}>()
- CSS variables for theming — never hardcoded color values
- Always :key on v-for loops
